features: ♥ New Retractable Dog Leash - Does your dog often chew the dog leash? It's very unsanitary. Our dog leash comes with extra strong chains to prevent your dog from biting the nylon dogleash. Fresh and natural color, relax your mood and enjoy walking your dog. ▲【TIPS: Heavy-duty retractable dog lead with chain lead are not suitable for puppies and small dogs, thank you for your kind.】

♥ Easy One Button Control: The reliable braking system of the extendable dog leash for small dog makes the dog leash for large dogs easy to brake and lock whenever and wherever you need. Just press the control button on the dog leash to free or lock it by pushing forward/backward with your thumb. It gives you full control to ensure the safety of your dog and the public.

♥ Durable Nylon Dog Leash: Made of eco-friendly and durable rope and ABS plastic casing, the heavy-duty retractable dog leash for large dogs offers strong enough for dogs up to 50kg. The extendable dog leash 5m can be extended up to 5 m. This allows you to adjust the dog leash to a comfortable length and give your dogs more freedom to wander, sniff, and stab.

♥ Comfortable Handle Design: Ergonomic handle and non-slip silicone handle feels good in your hand, easy to control and safe enough no matter your dog is pulling or running. This 360° tangle-free retractable dog leash for medium dogs can effectively prevent winding and knotting, and the built-in stainless steel elastic spring can endure traction about 30,000 times for a long time.

♥ Great Quality and Warm Service: What will you get? 1 x retractable dog leash, 1 x stainless steel chain, 1 x portable bag dispenser (including a roll of bin bag). Exactly carefree for you. For any questions or advice about our extendable dog leash for small, medium and large dogs, contact us instantly.
description: Product Description ABOUT ETECHDRA Etechydra is committed to producing safe, durable, comfortable and beautiful pet supplies. We have a year of sales experience and we are constantly improving our products to provide our customers with a better experience. Why Choose Etechydra Dog Retractable Leash Lead? One year of pet supplies sales experience, we are constantly improving ourselves. - Durable traction heavy duty dog rope - The sturdy dog steel chain perfectly matches the dog leash. - Reinforced metal hook, strong and durable, not easy to rust - ABS+TPE material, safe and friendly, wear-resistant, long-term use. - Ergonomically designed non-slip handle, safe and reliable, can be held comfortably for a long time. - The 360°tangle-free retractable dog leash is flexible and easy to use. The Retractable Dog Leash Is Designed For Walking In Open Areas With Your Best Friend To Enjoy The Fun Of Freedom. Strong Dog Tape for Safe Use Adpoted Nylon material, stronger and smoother. 16ft can provide comfort and maximum freedom for your pet in safe condition. Durable Rustproof Swivel Hook Durable rustproof swivel hook can tightly chains up the pet and can safely protect your pet from impacting. Easy to Use & Quick Brake & Lock Simply use your green dog leash, push forward with your thumb to release the rope, and push backward to lock the rope. Strong Dog Leash with Anti-Chewing Steel Chain It's more durable & safer when paired with a strong chain, so you don't have to worry about your dog biting the dog rope. Warm Tips: Give Your Cute Dog A Gift Dog Leash To Run Free & Safely. 1. The dog lead rope can be used with steel chains or used alone. 2. After use, it is recommended to remove the steel chain and shrink the nylon rope first, so as to avoid the rebound of the steel chain causing injury. 3. Don’t allow children to use the leash. Never try to open the plastic casing, disassemble any other parts. 4. For safety, the 16-inch retractable dog leash is recommended for cats and dogs under 90 pounds.
